I often times hear many well-meaning believers talk about the anointing as if everything is anointed. Can I loving say, if everything is anointed than nothing is.😳🤔

Some things happen as a result of hard work, a gift you’ve worked at, a skill—but the anointing is supernatural and comes on you/through you to manifest the Kingdom of God—heal the sick, cast out demons, prophecy, preach the Gospel, etc…

We need to be sure our definitions come from Scripture, over experience. God Presence is with all believers, but His anointing comes with an assignment that matches what Jesus carried—we are His followers.

Reinhard Bonnke said, “Often times we are looking for the anointing, when God is waiting for us to say something he can anoint!”🔥

Luke 22:29, Isaiah 61, Acts 1:8, Acts 10:38
